commit.message:
Setup Token POST

Made when user is created to setup a token to write to the DB for push notifications in the future.

Fixed some sign up process

We fixed the process for setting up notifications. Also removed some old unneeded XML stuff, and JAVA docs. To get rid of potential errors.

Upbring, Got all devices done.

We got the app fully functional. Now working on integrating better UI/UX, then working on custom notifications.

Assigned user luggage

We assigned the user luggage APIs to post into the DB. Now working on getting all of the bluetooth setup.
